    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "Wine list\nJAL EXECUTIVE CLASS\n•• SEASONS",
      "TOKYO — SAN FRANCISCO\nWESTERN\nAmuse-Gueule\nSmoked Duck \"Balsamico\" Style\nAppetizer\nMarinated Seafood Tuna Sauce\nSalad\nFresh Salad / Tarragon Dressing\nStewed Ox Tongue\nNoodles / Assorted Vegetables\n1309 kcal.)I\nMain Dish (Choice)\nJAL Healthy Menu Selection\nFillet of Sole Bonne Femme\nRoSUllEU Veselauies\n(10 x6dl.)\nSpecial Bread or Steamed Rice\nDessert Wagon (Choice)\nFrench Pastries / Ice Cream / Fresh Fruits\nAssorted Cheese / Chocolate\nBeverage\nCoffee\nTea\nGreen Tea\nWe apologize if occasionally your choice is not available.\nLight and well-balanced\ndish which is low in fat\nalla ball\nTOKYO — SAN FRANCISCO\nJAPANESE\nAppetizer\nConger Eel in Jelly / Simmered \"Yuba\" Roll\nSimmered Green Vegetable / Simmered Shrimp with Ginger\nMixed Squid \u0026 Cucumber with Miso-Vinegar Dressing\nNimono\nDeep-Simmered Fried Pork with Vegetables\nSunomono\nMixed Seafood with Vinegar Dressing\nDainomono\nGrilled Salmon / Glazed Chestnut\nKobachi\nBoiled Spinach \u0026 Whitebait in Light Soy Sauce\nMiso Soup\nSteamed Rice\nDessert Wagon (Choice)\nFrench Pastries / Ice Cream / Fresh Fruits\nAssorted Cheese / Chocolate\nCoffee\nBeverage\nTea\nGreen Tea\nwe apologize it occasionally your cnoice is not avallabie."
